&gt; &gt; word changed to &#39;hardware&#39; in the same voice, that would suggest actual phonetic 
&gt; &gt; manipulation. Somy question: is there any good evidence of that sort of manipulation?
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; I keep using the phrase &#39;good evidence&#39; to mean high quality sound that is easily
&gt; &gt; understood without having to strain one&#39;s ears. The sample you gave in this
